ciated with\nprior specifications for the data-model discrepancy. Also, using the\nunaggregated data results in sharper projections based on our climate model.\nOur computationally efficient approach may be widely applicable to a variety of\nhigh-dimensional computer model calibration problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Mar 2013 16:44:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Oct 2013 21:36:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 7 Feb 2014 00:38:18 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 12 Feb 2014 18:20:12 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 31 Jul 2014 10:45:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-08-01"}
